  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK223">
<l>ilaṉeṉṉu mevva muraiyāmai yītal</l>
<l>kulaṉuṭaiyāṉ kaṇṇē uḷa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(Even in a low state) not to adopt the mean expedient of saying "I have nothing," but to give, is the characteristic of the mad of noble birth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
